This page is meant for my great friends back at UofT



I figure its best to have as much information for everyone to learn from for free. All of these links are websites I found which pertain to courses at UofT. If you have found any more, let me know and Il add them to this website. As well, I might pair these up with historical averages. If you have data related to this, please let me know. Also if you think you know of a better colour for the links, send me an email. Im not sure im entirely happy with the gray.
